query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `debateResults` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `debateId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `finalAssessment` text,
  `synthesis` text,
  `moderatorTopPick` varchar(64),
  `moderatorReasoning` text,
  `peerVotes` json,
  `strongestArguments` json,
  `devilsAdvocateSuccess` boolean DEFAULT false,
  `pointsAwarded` json,
  `roundCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `topicTags` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `debateResults_debateId_unique` (`debateId`)
);
